    <p>
        This <a target="_blank" href="https://www.syncfusion.com/aspnet-mvc-ui-controls/charts/chart-types/step-area-chart">ASP.NET MVC Step Area Chart</a> example visualizes electricity generation data using renewable and non-renewable resources in a step area chart.
    </p>
